{"tid":54723,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分左手一排後 自信左開心咗","createTime":"2016-12-25T18:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T00:53:43.000Z","uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f954d31c4c0cfb80c8a6461be0e588f8b1d53231","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:45:07.000Z","msg":"最初我都喊死<br />\n後來兩個月後發現自己<br />\n又自信開心 有目標左<br />\n<br />\n（轉自內容農場）<br />\n這項發表在 Journal of Personal Relationships 的研究調查 92 名最近剛經歷分手的在學學生。<br />\n<br />\n第一項有趣的發現是，每個受測者都列出分手後人生正向的改變，平均約有 5 個正向的轉變。<br />\n<br />\n有些分手後正向改變的例子包括覺得更有自信、獨立或與家人和朋友更親密。<br />\n<br />\n或許很難想像在經歷這麼痛苦的分手後你會變得更快樂，但這是真的。放手把讓不屬於你的愛情離開，才能遠離傷痛，然後從中學習些什麼。放手讓曾經打擊我們的人事物離開後，變得更堅強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/vidaorange/2015/05/20/people-go-painful-breakups-end-stronger-happier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fvidaorange%2F2015%2F05%2F20%2Fpeople-go-painful-breakups-end-stronger-happier%2F&d=6skEbpnF%2FXtZDxY%2F7yju5GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7fa56305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/vidaorange/2015/05/20/people-go-painful-breakups-end-stronger-happier/</a>"},{"pid":"9cc3f093f99cf0f6a2abdaa668a9ba5cc5e10af7","tid":54723,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"363d943d21b822a724da9b2456ad42431e94d6be","tid":54723,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:46:47.000Z","msg":"真絲？"},{"pid":"c2c16437b989d61da971870399c6dec9e318bcfc","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:47:49.000Z","msg":"我真係好辛苦 當初<br />\n溝通唔到既人遲早都係散<br />\n唔解決溝通問題 /嘈交多番逃避<br />\n唔代表ok 只係我係度忍耐忍耐再忍耐"},{"pid":"5c97e5cb42ce315e81ab4d048dd9004b3ce71106","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"絲 梗係絲<br />\n巴打應該難放開啲 比起女仔"},{"pid":"8ec15abf7ce675e1d41eb83ef51395