左 難信人"},{"pid":"489c6a013e30966bffb1d5b7e63d481d09300be6","tid":54723,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:56:03.000Z","msg":"多謝哂你D正能量，提醒起我自己想分下都冇得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02a8820abfe7ddd5b8466c4b64c9f2ae70e4bae","tid":54723,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前日散左 完全唔知點走出傷痛 <br />\n無時無刻都諗翻我同佢d野 晚晚訓覺都流幾滴馬尿<br />\n以後真係怕撚左拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先幾日 就儘量比自己發洩下<br />\n你呢啲係新鮮滾熱辣傷口<br />\n我果陣頭一個月都sad緊<br />\n始終無左個親密無間既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚心痛啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a560a5e31beaab361ba18eff0cb7b3bfbf3f50","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前日散左 完全唔知點走出傷痛 <br />\n無時無刻都諗翻我同佢d野 晚晚訓覺都流幾滴馬尿<br />\n以後真係怕撚左拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先幾日 就儘量比自己發洩下<br />\n你呢啲係新鮮滾熱辣傷口<br />\n我果陣頭一個月都sad緊<br />\n始終無左個親密無間既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚心痛啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要快啲走出情傷<br />\n最初一定要發洩晒 盡情地<br />\n可以避免慢慢以後陣痛感覺<br />\n<br />\n我一分手狂睇啲情傷雞精書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b81a7ada5cb8fc1aea4b9daec48915eeffccf20","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係自信左加開心左<br />\n不過個人負面左 難信人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nclick入去睇成篇文 巴打<br />\n我copy啲俾你睇<br />\n<br />\nMaya Angelou 曾說：<br />\n<br />\n一定要有足夠的勇氣再去相信愛，而且要一再相信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當我們走出心碎、不好的戀愛、可怕的分手後，會感受到兩種截然不同的世界。我們已經知道愛可以多美好，也有多輕易變得遙不可及。"},{"pid":"67365aa27777d62e71850675553dd67e1d7a2cdb","tid":54723,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先幾日 就儘量比自己發洩下<br />\n你呢啲係新鮮滾熱辣傷口<br />\n我果陣頭一個月都sad緊<br />\n始終無左個親密無間既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚心痛啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要快啲走出情傷<br />\n最初一定要發洩晒 盡情地<br />\n可以避免慢慢以後陣痛感覺<br />\n<br />\n我一分手狂睇啲情傷雞精書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6e597783c5cce6c6c8f6662dbb34d844e49358","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"我睇愛情心理 想知點解分手咁撚心痛<br />\n《如果，愛能不寂寞》呢啲<br />\n<br />\n但最初我上網睇文章治療先<br />\ngoogle '分手' 已經大把<br />\n鄺俊宇啲mk文都好幫手認真"},{"pid":"03ff543ca2aa7b461887c4b8f062f2232840e8c2","tid":54723,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇愛情心理 想知點解分手咁撚心痛<br />\n《如果，愛能不寂寞》呢啲<br />\n<br />\n但最初我上網睇文章治療先<br />\ngoogle '分手' 已經大把<br />\n鄺俊宇啲mk文都好幫手認真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以話 分手只係一個逗號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab08384736e35891d65b93d723367d8ec67db5f","tid":54723,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:49:32.000Z","msg":"me too <br />\n分左手個人冇咁毒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qvpo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qvpo.gif&h=b1b99178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfed887ab75ddea403ebd9d43aa40df98de5e8e3","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:53:26.000Z","msg":"毒撚咪留負評<br />\n你對人生悲觀唔關我事<br />\n乜嘢都諗到咁負面<br />\n我開個post鼓勵分手者振作又以為我針對你<br />\n毒撚啲性格真係好乞人憎<br />\n平日又自私猛咁講自己 唔撚識雙向溝通<br />\n回應朋友<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"f13bf8268147cb33146b1a8ff313e6b622381b53","tid":54723,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me too <br />\n分左手個人冇咁毒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qvpo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qvpo.gif&h=b1b99178&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3163534590d950d064c9c2e75b0da874e2a6cae3","tid":54723,"uid":23368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"好難忘記，亦有好多無謂既比較出左黎<br />\n亦多左好多猜疑"},{"pid":"bb7293e56b6e47ec37d5093b89a61e2feb423c3f","tid":54723,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T20:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>me too <br />\n分左手個人冇咁毒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Qvpo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Qvpo.gif&h=b1b99178&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試 同 學多左新野 識多左朋友 但仲未識到新女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901c657d926d714733b7c9542a85b3e90e3eabae","tid":54723,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"拍左拖就真係自信左開心左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}